<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rebel Wilson has been on a health and fitness journey this year, losing at least 18kg (40lbs or 2.8 stone).</p>

<p>And on Friday, the Australian actress was jumping for joy as she flaunted her shrinking frame in a photo shared to Instagram. </p>

<p>The 40-year-old revealed her slimmed down pins in black exercise leggings as she posed in front of a fountain in New York. </p>

<p>Thrilled: Rebel Wilson, 40, (pictured) was jumping for joy as she flaunted her shrinking frame in a photo shared to Instagram on Friday, following her astonishing 18kg weight loss </p>

<p>Rebel added a black jumper and trendy Moschino bag to the look, while sweeping her blonde locks back under a cap. </p>

<p>She wore minimal makeup, allowing her natural beauty to shine through. </p>

<p>'Recreating ISN'T IT ROMANTIC in Central Park today and rocking a bum bag like a BOSS,' she captioned the picture. </p>

<p>'Year of health': Rebel Wilson has been on an incredible health and fitness journey this year, losing at least 18kg</p>

<p>The Pitch Perfect star also shared the photo to her Instagram Stories. </p>

<p>Last month, Rebel highlighted her weight loss as she shared several photos to Instagram of her slimmer frame in a tight blue wrap dress.  </p>

<p>The Australian actress explained that she is inching closer and closer to her goal of 75kg. </p>

<p>Blue beauty! Last month, Rebel showed off her slimmed down physique in a tight blue wrap dress on Instagram (left). Pictured on the right in May 2019  </p>

<p>'Thanks for all the love so far on my 'Year of Health' journey,' she captioned the post. </p>

<p>'When I was reaching for the candies last night after dinner I thought to myself 'hmmmm...better not' and had a bottle of water instead.'  </p>

<p>She added: '8kg's to go until I hit my goal - hopefully I can do it by the end of the year.' </p>

<p>Getting into shape: The post comes after she announced in January that she was going to make her health a priority in 2020</p>

<p>The post comes after she announced in January that she was going to make her health a priority in 2020.</p>

<p>'So for me 2020 is going to be called 'The Year of Health'. So I put on the athleisure and went out for a walk, deliberately hydrating on the couch right now,' she told her Instagram followers.</p>

<p>'And [I'm] trying to avoid the sugar and junk food, which is going to be hard after the holidays I've just had but I'm going to do it!'</p>

<p>In May, Rebel revealed she was trying to get down to her goal weight of 75kg (165lbs or 11.8 stone). </p>

<p>Kilo by kilo: Rebel revealed in May that she was trying to get down to her goal weight of 75kg (165lbs or 11.8 stone)</p>
